      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A derailment has interrupted the trains operating on the Coastal Line, Ada Derana correspondent says.",
        "As per reports, the \u2018Rajarata Rejina\u2019 passenger train, en route from Vavuniya to Beliatta, stalled near the Ambalangoda railway station this afternoon."
